'''Olivier Vatine''' is a French artist, best known to ''[[Star Wars]]'' audiences as the penciler of the [[Dark Horse Comics]] adaptation of [[Timothy Zahn]]'s [[Heir to the Empire (comics)|''Heir to the Empire'']] and as the cover artist of the [[Dark Horse Books]] trade paperback ''[[Star Wars Rebels (TPB)|Star Wars Rebels]]''.{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by Olivier Vatine}}

